data.description: Welcome to this spacious and modern 5-bedroom, 3-bath home nestled in the desirable Bridgewater community of Lakeland. Boasting a newer build, this immaculate residence offers the ideal setting for a large family seeking comfort and convenience. Step inside to discover an inviting and open floor plan, featuring generous living spaces, a well-appointed kitchen with contemporary finishes, and plenty of room to entertain. The five bedrooms provide ample space for everyone to have their own retreat, while the three bathrooms ensure convenience and privacy. Enjoy the perks of community living with access to Bridgewater's amenities, including a sparkling pool for those hot Florida days, a serene dock for waterfront relaxation, and a playground to keep the little ones entertained.
